content.rendered:
File Upload

There are some situations where we may require you to send us large files to help with quoting, technical support, printing services, and so on. We have set up this page to simplify the process for you.


How To Send Us Your Files

We use wetransfer.com to send/receive large files. We’ve found it simple to use and it’s free.

But first

  • Please use the thinglab@freedspace.com.au email address to send the files to
  • We prefer Zip files, if you can compress them that would be great. If not, that’s ok too
  • To make sure we know who the file belongs to please include your name, phone number and the company name in your message

Now you are ready

Go to wetransfer.com to send your file(s)
